title: Ep. 18 - Space Exploration
itunes:title: Ep. 18 - Space Exploration
description: Sometimes we all need a little space — from our kids, from our partner, from a friend — but who hasn’t been just a little hurt when someone has said they need some space? Giving and asking for space can be a good thing. So give yourself some space to hear what Wendy’s thinking about alone time and infinite possibility.
